f09d4cfb-a1c7-4848-a444-24902bd7b793.title: Vannaka
f09d4cfb-a1c7-4848-a444-24902bd7b793.text: 'Ello, and what are you after then?

options.text: Have you any rewards for me, or anything to trade?
Let's talk about the difficulty of my assignments.

f76a2863-ea20-4dc9-a71e-6ad151441cf0.title: Vannaka
f76a2863-ea20-4dc9-a71e-6ad151441cf0.text:
You are too low of a combat level, come back when,
you are more experienced.

f1916800-a42c-4bf5-8895-8534dc0e488e.title: Vannaka
f1916800-a42c-4bf5-8895-8534dc0e488e.text:
You're still meant to be slaying <slayer_task_type>(s),
you have <slayer_task_remaining> to go.

b674ceeb-5529-4ecc-869f-2cb89a9e6302.title: <player>
b674ceeb-5529-4ecc-869f-2cb89a9e6302.text: Have you any rewards for me, or anything to trade?

ced06123-ce36-4cda-80b6-ac5919624e04.title: Vannaka
ced06123-ce36-4cda-80b6-ac5919624e04.text:
I have quite a few rewards you can earn, and a wide
variety of Slayer equipment for sale.

061945ed-1e69-4b28-ba17-beaa77792b7e.title: <player>
061945ed-1e69-4b28-ba17-beaa77792b7e.text: Let's talk about the difficulty of my assignments.

5b2ced75-9074-46b3-b75d-403633c89ac0.title: Vannaka
5b2ced75-9074-46b3-b75d-403633c89ac0.text:
The Slayer Masters will take your combat level into
account when choosing tasks for you, so you shouldn't
get anything too hard.

824438bf-5ec1-428b-83f6-f4eb3f4105a6.title: <player>
824438bf-5ec1-428b-83f6-f4eb3f4105a6.text: That's fine - I don't want anything too tough.
